				</div>
				
				p.row
					h2.col-md-12 With us you can:
					.col-md-6
						h3 Calculate your monthly/early deposit
						img.img-responsive(src="/images/deposited.png",alt="monthly deposit")
						
					.col-md-6
						h3 To know your successful Rank
